Interface OrderShipmentProductIf

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OrderShipmentProduct

    public interface OrderShipmentProductIf
    OrderShipmentProduct object. It points to an OrderProduct object but has a quantity attribute to keep track of how many products were shipped.
